item.title: CVE-2023-5211|2023-10-31T13:54:45.520Z -- unknown -- fattura24
item.description: The Fattura24 WordPress plugin before 6.2.8 does not sanitize or escape the 'id' parameter before outputting it back in the page, leading to a reflected Cross-Site Scripting vulnerability.
